The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.LG", "cs.AI", "cs.NE", and "cs.IR". 

- "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and reading comprehension. 
- "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a neural architecture for the task. 
- "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with a task that requires AI techniques. 
- "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper uses a neural architecture. 
- "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the task involves extracting information from a document.
